               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470705-name-824" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-824" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-824" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-824" type="given" value="STEPHEN"></interp>STEPHEN SMITH.</persName>
                  </hi> I live with my father, Isaac Smith, who keeps the Half Moon public-house, in Smithfield. On the 30th of June, I was at the National Baths, at Lambeth—I undressed myself—I missed my boots in two or three minutes afterwards—these are them—they are my father's—I lost them about four o'clock.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did you see me take them? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No.</p>
